# Contributing to {{metadata.name}} SDK

Thank you for your interest in this project!

## Important: This SDK is Auto-Generated

This SDK is automatically generated from the Blackboard Learn REST API specification
using the [Blackboard Learn SDK Generator](https://github.com/blackboard/blackboard-learn-sdk-generator).
**Do not submit pull requests to this repository** — changes will be overwritten on
the next generation run.

## How to Contribute

### Report Bugs

If you find a bug, please open an issue in this repository. Include:

- Steps to reproduce the problem
- Expected vs actual behavior
- SDK version: `{{metadata.version}}`
- Your runtime version and operating system

### Request Features

For feature requests (new API methods, better types, improved error handling, etc.),
open an issue describing what you'd like to see. Feature requests that affect the
generated code will be implemented in the generator and released in a future SDK version.

### Report API Spec Issues

If you notice incorrect or missing API definitions (wrong parameter types, missing
endpoints, etc.), please open an issue. These may be upstream spec issues that need
to be reported to Blackboard.

## Development

Since this SDK is auto-generated, local development is only useful for testing
or experimentation. Any changes you make locally will not persist across SDK
version updates.

